  <name>TeaTime Accessibility (Photosensitive)</name>
  <summary>Photosensitive-safe tea timer with large buttons and statistics</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A photosensitive-safe version of the TeaTime Accessibility timer. All visual effects that could potentially trigger seizures have been removed.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>No flashing or color-changing effects</li>
      <li>No animated visual transitions or sprites</li>
      <li>Large, clear display with adjustable font size</li>
      <li>Stable, consistent visual design</li>
      <li>Sound notifications and statistics tracking</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
